This project depends on third-party software with separate licenses,
distributed at runtime (not bundled in this repository) or vendored at build
time. The relevant ones:

- Retro68 cross-compiler — MIT-style, see https://github.com/autc04/Retro68
- Infinite Mac (BasiliskII WASM build) — Apache License 2.0, see
  https://github.com/mihaip/infinite-mac. When BasiliskII WASM artifacts are
  redistributed (e.g. embedded in the GitHub Pages deployment), the Apache 2.0
  NOTICE file must accompany them.
- Basilisk II emulator — GPL v2+, see http://basilisk.cebix.net. Used in
  binary form via Infinite Mac's WebAssembly build.
- Apple System 7.5.5 — freely redistributable per Apple's 1996 release. Not
  bundled in this repository; loaded at runtime from Infinite Mac's CDN.
